Saenz, Appellee, v. Industrial Commission of Ohio et al., Appellants.

[Cite as Saenz v. Indus. Comm. (1993), 68 Ohio St.3d 108.]

(No. 92-1755 Submitted November 10, 1993 Decided December 29, 1993.) Gallon & Takacs Co., L.P.A, and Theodore A. Bowman, for appellee. *109Lee I. Fisher, Attorney General, Diane J. Karpinski and Cash Mischka, Assistant Attorneys General, for appellants.

The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed on authority of State ex rel. Brown v. Indus. Comm. (1993), 68 Ohio St.3d 45, 623 N.E.2d 55.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur. Wright, J.,

dissents for the reasons stated in his dissent in State ex rel. Brown v. Indus. Comm. (1993), 68 Ohio St.3d 45, 50, 623 N.E.2d 55, 59.
